{
  "texts": [
    "To construct a new family of motifs fulfilling the structural properties required in Conjecture 1.4 of [CGV25]; 2.",
    "To prove that an algorithm based on counting such motifs successfully recovers the communities above the threshold (2).",
    "These results complement the contributions of [Chi+25] and [CGV25], and together establish that the computational barrier for community recovery in the SBM with K ≥ √ n communities lies at (2).",
    "Moreover, they indicate that the optimal algorithms in this regime appear to be unrelated to spectral methods, echoing similar observations made for Gaussian mixture models [EGV24].",
    "Organisation and notation."
  ]
}